                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 312.52/682.</note>
                <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Torreon</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-10-21">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 21, 1915</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Department’s October 8. See my October 13 and October 21. This Government desires
                    to deal directly with representatives of foreign governments accredited to this
                    Government. Will Department inform me what further action is desired relative to
                    these representations on behalf of Spanish and other foreign interests?</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">John W. Belt.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
